# 去掉猪皮之后先切成片
Remove the skin and slice it

0:01:24.250,0:01:26.150
# 然后再剁成肉泥备用
Then cut it to grounded meat

0:01:37.925,0:01:39.275
# 下一步开始调味
Then start marinating the meat

0:01:39.400,0:01:40.875
# 碗中加入食用盐1勺
Add a spoon of salt to the bowl

0:01:41.475,0:01:42.875
# 加入少许胡椒粉
Add a little ground pepper

0:01:43.350,0:01:44.950
# 加入生抽酱油3克
Add 3g of soy sauce

0:01:47.200,0:01:48.575
# 加入少许老抽调底色
Add some dark soy sauce for the color

0:01:52.800,0:01:54.100
# 然后将猪肉搅拌均匀
Then mix the meat with the sauces

0:01:54.350,0:01:56.000
# 这一步的目的是上劲
This allows the meat to come together

0:02:00.650,0:02:03.200
# 猪肉上劲之后再加入1个鸡蛋搅拌均匀
Then add an egg and mix properly

0:02:15.600,0:02:18.075
# 最后再加入少许玉米淀粉拌匀备用
Finally add some corn starch to mix and set aside

0:02:28.475,0:02:29.600
# 下一步开始制作
Then start cooking

0:02:29.950,0:02:32.200
# 首先我们在苦瓜圈中抹上干淀粉
First, apply some starch to the inner side of the ring-shaped bitter gourds

0:02:32.275,0:02:34.275
# 这一步的目的是让肉泥粘的更稳
This is to allow the ground meat to stay in the ring

0:02:44.325,0:02:46.475
# 然后将调好味的肉泥酿入苦瓜中
Then add the marinated meat to the bitter gourds

0:02:46.575,0:02:48.525
# 同学们可以尽量的多加一些肉末
More meat is better

0:02:48.775,0:02:50.675
# 这样能够使苦瓜更加的饱满
Because it makes the final product more rich

0:02:55.900,0:02:58.300
# 然后在酿好的肉末两边粘上干淀粉备用
Then apply starch on the two sides of the meat

0:02:58.500,0:03:01.475
# 粘干淀粉的目的是防止两面煎的时候粘连
Starch prevents the two sides from sticking together when it's fried

0:03:16.000,0:03:17.750
# 下一步我们开始调碗汁
Next, we start to prepare the sauce

0:03:17.950,0:03:19.775
# 碗中加入生抽酱油5克
Add 5g of soy sauce to the bowl

0:03:21.375,0:03:22.750
# 加入蚝油3克
Add 3g of oyster sauce

0:03:25.450,0:03:26.675
# 加入少许白糖
Add a little sugar

0:03:27.650,0:03:29.000
# 加入食用盐1勺
Add a spoon of salt

0:03:29.775,0:03:31.275
# 加入清汤40克
Add 40g of clear broth

0:03:34.350,0:03:36.825
# 最后加入适量的干淀粉（土豆淀粉）搅拌均匀备用
Finally add some potato starch and mix it properly

0:03:39.200,0:03:40.600
# 下一步开始制作
Next, start pan-frying

0:03:40.775,0:03:42.200
# 首先我们把锅烧热
First we heat up the wok

0:03:42.300,0:03:44.375
# 锅烧热之后加入适量的油滑锅
When the wok is heated, add some oil to the wok

0:03:47.500,0:03:49.300
# 滑好锅之后将热油倒出
Then pour the oil out

0:03:51.050,0:03:52.700
# 然后加入少许的底油
Now add some base oil

0:03:53.800,0:03:56.004
# 油温4成热之后依次下入苦瓜
When it's 40% heated, add the bitter gourds one by one

0:04:11.250,0:04:12.975
# 然后开小火煎8分钟
Then turn to low heat for 8 minutes

0:04:13.075,0:04:15.500
# 同学们切记必须小火慢慢煎
Keep in mind we need low heat

0:04:15.650,0:04:17.800
# 不能开大火否则很容易煎糊
Because high heat easily burns the bitter gourds

0:04:18.000,0:04:19.700
# 正所谓慢工出细活
Patience is the best practice

0:04:19.775,0:04:21.800
# 中途用筷子将其翻面煎香
Midway, flip the bitter gourds to pan-fry the other side

0:04:34.275,0:04:38.100
# 两面煎香之后转中火然后缓缓加入调好的碗汁
When both sides are ready, turn to mid heat and slowly pour in the prepared sauce

0:04:48.975,0:04:50.800
# 碗汁下锅之后转中小火
Then turn to mid-low heat

0:04:50.875,0:04:52.850
# 将汤汁收浓即可出锅装盘
When the sauce becomes condensed, it's ready to be served

